  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">9 pages, 7 figures, Contribution to the Topical Issue "Perspectives on Nuclear Data for the Next Decade" edited by N. Alamanos, E. Bauge, and S. Hilaire</subfield>
    <subfield code="9">arXiv</subfield>
