    <subfield code="y">00005 Moment of inertia $I$ versus excitation energy $E_x$ for the nuclei $^{55}$Fe, $^{56}$Fe and $^{60}$Co. The moment of inertia $I$ extracted from $\sigma^2$ using Eq.~(\ref{sigma-I}) (solid squares with error bars) is compared with the rigid-body moment of inertia (dashed lines). Adapted from Ref.~\cite{Alhassid2007}.</subfield>
